            <fr:title text="invertible maps are contractible"><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" title="Inverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" type="local">invertible</fr:link> maps are <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001T/" title="n-truncated map" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001T/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001T/" type="local">contractible</fr:link></fr:title>
